{"attribution":"Occupational Safety and Health Administration, Fallen Workers Brochure, 2023, Chinese Simplified; no OSHA or U.S. Department of Labor endorsement or affiliation is implied.","cases":[{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-001","input":"来自 Tonya Ford的信息 OSHA家庭联络员亲人的离世是一个家庭最痛苦的事情之一。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-001","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-002","input":"我在 2009 年的一次职业事故中失去了一位亲人，因此我了解并理解你们所遭受的直接打击。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-002","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-003","input":"请在您方便的时候与我联系。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-003","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-004","input":"我希望通过帮助您解决有关您亲人的事故、检查过程、工人纪念日和/或 OSHA 的任何问题，来减轻您的一些担忧。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-004","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-005","input":"OSHA 对您的损失深表遗憾。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-005","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-006","input":"我们将竭诚为您服务。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-006","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-007","input":"哀伤的常见阶段：否认、愤怒、纠结、抑郁、接受照顾好自己。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-007","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-008","input":"分享/创建纪念物品或活动。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-008","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-009","input":"承认你的失落和哀伤感情。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-009","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-010","input":"专注于可以掌控的生活方面。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-010","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-011","input":"OSHA 设立了一个虚拟的工人纪念墙，以纪念在工作中失去生命的同事。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-011","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-012","input":"22 个州计划（21 个州和波多黎各）既包括私营企业，也包括州和地方政府部门。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-012","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-013","input":"其他 7 个州计划（康涅狄格州、伊利诺伊州、缅因州、马萨诸塞州、新泽西州、纽约州和维尔京群岛）仅涵盖州和地方政府工作人员。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-013","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-014","input":"须知和期望 OSHA 将对您亲人的事故进行调查，以确定是否违反了 OSHA 规定。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-014","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-015","input":"我们在六个月内完成调查，希望你理解。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-015","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-016","input":"所有罚金将直接上缴美国财政部；它们不会被当做OSHA 预算或收入。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-016","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-017","input":"OSHA 不会仅仅因为工作场所发生死亡事故就发出违规通知。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-017","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-018","input":"您可以与当地的 OSHA 办事处联系，询问案件的进展情况或提出问题。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-018","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-019","input":"如果你能提供有助于检查的信息或证据，请通过写信、打电话或发电子邮件的方式与当地 OSHA 办事处分享。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-019","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-020","input":"检查结束后，地区主管将回答你的问题并解释处理方案。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-020","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-021","input":"OSHA 将在结案时通知你。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-021","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-022","input":"《信息自由法案》（FOIA）规定了 OSHA 事故检查信息的发布。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-022","split":"document"}},{"classification":{"domain":null,"risk":null,"status":"needs_input_only_review"},"id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1/sentence-023","input":"在案件结案后，根据书面申请， OSHA 将向您提供根据《信息自由法》可以公开的部分检查档案，您作为家庭成员无需支付任何费用。","provenance":{"raw_url":"https://www.osha.gov/sites/default/files/publications/FALLEN-WORKERS-BROCHURE-2023-ZH-SI.pdf","source_case_id":"sentence-023","split":"document"}}],"converter_output_used":false,"dataset":"blind-v2","id":"osha-fallen-workers-family-simplified-v1","input_only":true,"license":"U.S. Public Domain","modification_notice":"Extracted complete Simplified Chinese sentences from the checksum-pinned OSHA PDF, excluded URLs, phone and crisis-line instructions, email addresses, page furniture, images, logos, external organizations, and other third-party content, and added input-only provenance; no expected text or converter output was used.","purpose":"candidate_source_pilot","review_policy":"domain_and_risk_must_be_assigned_from_input_only","source_class":"public_domain","stats":{"by_split":{"document":23},"eligible_pending_review":23,"exclusions":{},"raw_cases":23},"upstream_revision":"OSHA 2023, Fallen Workers Brochure, Chinese Simplified; retrieved PDF SHA-256: 9af69756e3640e385f51a13825bce70110faa340b5e8f163e779d582a3f2c213","version":1}
